Package: miRHeat
Type: Package
Title: Tools for 'miRNA' and 'UTR' Interaction Filtering and Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-06-24
Authors@R: 
    c(
      person(
        given = "Maria",
        family = "Nicoletti",
        email = "maria.nicoletti@unesp.br",
        role = c("aut", "cre")
      )
    )
Description: Tools to process, filter and visualize 'miRNA' and 'UTR' interaction predictions.
    Includes functions to parse 'RNAhybrid' or 'IntaRNA' output files, filter by
    interaction energy and seed pairing, and convert results into tidy data frames
    and heatmaps for comparative visualization.
